Wave 8 polish on the Set Action dialog: validation icons + Recent dropdown arrow now use theme-aware QStyle pixmaps that adapt to dark mode (the previous hex stylesheets blew out in dark theme), the validation icon is hidden when the error label is visible (uncluttering the regex row), splitter handle position persists across reopens with a wider 8px grab target, and a new "Reset window size" button (or Ctrl+0) clears persisted geometry without touching mode/field/simple_op preferences (#349, #350, #351).
